      • exportTableAsCSV

        public static void exportTableAsCSV(JComponent parent,
                                    boolean visibleOnly,
                                    org.gephi.graph.api.Table table,
                                    boolean edgesTable,
                                    Character separator,
                                    Charset charset,
                                    Integer[] columnsToExport,
                                    String fileName)

        Exports a AttributeTable to a CSV file showing first a dialog to select the file to write.

        Parameters:
        parent - Parent window
        visibleOnly - Show only visible graph
        table - Table to export
        separator - Separator to use for separating values of a row in the CSV file. If null ',' will be used.
        charset - Charset encoding for the file
        columnsToExport - Indicates the indexes of the columns to export. All columns will be exported if null
